@startuml
' IOD(6)_Pj2_T-1 — User Story 6: Compare Semester Schedules
' Author: MayfairMI6

skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #444444
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #AAAAAA

title IOD(6)_Pj2_T-1\nUS6: Compare Semester Schedules

note right: Author: MayfairMI6

start

:Prerequisite: data for at least two semesters imported\n(see US1 — Upload Excel File);

:Actor navigates to the Compare Schedules Page;

:Actor selects Semester A from the first dropdown;
:Actor selects Semester B from the second dropdown;
note right: Semesters A and B must\nbe different

if (Same semester selected for both fields?) then (yes)
  :System alerts actor to select two different semesters;
  stop
else (no)
endif

:Actor clicks "Compare Schedules";

#ADD8E6:**ref** UC_COMPARE — Compare Semester Schedules
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
System identifies courses exclusive to Semester A,\nexclusive to Semester B, and common to both;

#ADD8E6:**ref** UC_STATS — View Semester Statistics
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
System computes total classes, unique courses,\nand total enrollment for each semester;

:System displays side-by-side comparison\nwith categorized course lists and summary statistics;

if (Actor selects a specific course for details?) then (yes)
  #ADD8E6:**ref** UC_DETAILS — View Class Details
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
  System shows section counts, enrollment,\nand a change summary for both semesters;
  :Actor reviews course-level detail;
else (no)
  :Actor reviews high-level comparison results;
endif

stop
@enduml
